_sText: Aim_ag_tyr ----------- 12 players+ Description: A symmetrical skill map set within a medium sized building. The objects are placed tactically so you can use it to your advantage. Both sides are exact mirrored. This is a texture map. I made this map to a design I quickly came up with and after toying around a bit it has worked out quite well. Objective: Fight your way through this symmetrical fortress and neutralize the threat that lies on the other side...
